  "scenarioDescription": "\n  <ul class=\"exoplanets-navigation-menu\">\n  <li><button href=\"#system\">System</button>\n  <li><button href=\"#GJ 3470\">Star</button>\n  <li><button href=\"#GJ 3470-b\">b</button></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1 id=\"system\">The GJ 3470 Exoplanetary System</h1>\n  <p>The GJ 3470 system contains 1 exoplanet. It is located 95.96 light years away from the solar system.</p>\n    <div class=\"celestial-object-wrapper\" id=\"GJ 3470\">\n  <section>\n  <h2>Star</h2>\n  <div class=\"size-comparison-wrapper\">\n  <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 100px; height: 100px; background-color: rgb(255, 242.3979365143785, 230.54885609599933);\">\n    <label>Sun</label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 55.00000000000001px; height: 55.00000000000001px; background-color: rgb(255, 195.33593672461836, 146.2593478218722)\">\n<label>GJ 3470</label>\n</div>\n</div>\n  </section>\n  <table cellspacing=\"0\">\n  <tr>\n    <td>Mass</td>\n    <td>0.54 solar masses</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Radius</td>\n    <td>0.55 solar radiae</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Temperature</td>\n    <td>3600 kelvin</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Stellar Metallicity</td>\n    <td>0.2 decimal exponent</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Age</td>\n    <td>1.65 billion years</td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n     \n    <div class=\"celestial-object-wrapper\" id=\"GJ 3470-b\">\n      <section>\n        <h2>GJ 3470-b</h2>\n        <p>    At more than 10 Earth masses, GJ 3470 b is an ice giant, a planet that is made up mostly of volatiles like water, amonia and methane, and enveloped by a dense hydrogen and helium atmosphere, much like Uranus and Neptune.  </p>\n        <div class=\"size-comparison-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px;\">\n            <label>Earth</label>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 45.7px; height: 45.7px;\">\n            <label>GJ 3470-b</label>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <table cellspacing=\"0\">\n          <tr>\n            <td>Mass</td>\n            <td>13.900 Earth masses</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Density</td>\n            <td>0.800 grams per cubic centimeter</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Radius</td>\n            <td>4.570 Earth radiae</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Semi-major Axis</td>\n            <td>0.0355 AU</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Eccentricity</td>\n            <td>0.017</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Orbital Period</td>\n            <td>3.337 days</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Method</td>\n            <td>Radial Velocity</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Facility</td>\n            <td>La Silla Observatory</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Telescope</td>\n            <td>3.6 m ESO Telescope</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Instrument</td>\n            <td>HARPS Spectrograph</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Date</td>\n            <td>2012-10</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Reference</td>\n            <td><a refstr=BONFILS_ET_AL__2012 href=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2012A%26A...546A..27B/abstract target=ref> Bonfils et al. 2012 </a></td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n      </section>\n    </div></a>\n  ",
